name: All The Hidden Quanta - Postcard from Lothlorien, Tawonga, Victoria - 2022/01/08
description:
The "All the Hidden Quanta - Postcard from ..." series using Processing visual arts language, explores the concept that we are surrounded by the unseen (unacknowledged? unrealised?), constantly in flux world of quanta. This project was processed from real time camera captures taken from the back porch at the Lothlorien BnB in Tawonga, Victoria, Australia. 
mp4, 1280x960px, 25fps, 22seconds(please loop), 38.2MB.
